 to souvenirs. But wait, don&#x2019;t buy your dinner at the market. Eat a Ceviche at <strong>Morena<\/strong> &#x2013; it will be the best one you have in Peru!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/things-to-do-cusco\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"the things to do in Cusco (opens in a new tab)\">the things to do in Cusco<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133733\/cusco-guide-San-Pedro-Market.jpg\" alt=\"cusco guide San Pedro Market\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cusco guide San Pedro Market\" class=\"wp-image-15507 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133733\/cusco-guide-San-Pedro-Market.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133733\/cusco-guide-San-Pedro-Market-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133733\/cusco-guide-San-Pedro-Market-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133733\/cusco-guide-San-Pedro-Market-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133733\/cusco-guide-San-Pedro-Market-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/upl