a of Cusco, the former Inca&#x2019;s empire. Explore the beautiful ruins of Pisac, Ollantaytambo, Moray, Saqsaywaman, Chinchero, or Maras Salt Mines.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Must-read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/peru-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Complete 3-week Peru Travel Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133642\/cusco-Moray-Ruins-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"cusco moray ruins\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cusco moray ruins\" data-id=\"15532\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=15532\" class=\"wp-image-15532 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133642\/cusco-Moray-Ruins-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133642\/cusco-Moray-Ruins-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133642\/cusco-Moray-Ruins-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133642\/cusco-Moray-Ruins-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133642\/cusco-Moray-Ruins-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/