hu\/\" target=\"_blank\">Machu Picchu<\/a>, the lost Incan city is a highlight of everyone&#x2019;s Peru trip. From Cusco, you are able to do a day trip by taking the scenic train ride from Ollantaytambo. However, if you want to see the sunrise at Machu Picchu, then head there one day in advance and spend the night in Aguas Calientes.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/machu-picchu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"everything about Machu Picchu in Peru (opens in a new tab)\">everything about Machu Picchu in Peru<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133716\/cusco-machu-picchu-peru-sunrise-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"machu picchu couple\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"machu picchu couple\" data-id=\"15517\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=15517\" class=\"wp-image-15517 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133716\/cusco-machu-picchu-peru-sunrise-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133716\/cusco-machu-picchu-peru-sunrise-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/